column2: Update tip of the day, fix invalid menu items, shortcuts, typos

column3:
I went through all tip of the day of IntelliJ Ultimate 12.1.1 and corrected a few mistakes.
Unfortunately a lot of images in the tips aren't displayed if I build IntelliJ Community Edition by myself
Environment: Windows 7 32 Bit, Java 6/7, latest source version from github
Failed: images/ctrl_shift_i_lookup.gif
Success: images/properties_completion.gif
The images are shown correctly if I use the packaged version from Jetbrains. Is this normal?
It would be nice if you would include this patch in one of the following releases.

Have you submitted a contributor license agreement? If not, please download the PDF from http://www.jetbrains.org/display/IJOS/Contributor+Agreement and then print it out, sign, scan and email to contribute@jetbrains.com
Yes, I have already submitted a contributor license agreement.
My pull request is probably outdated, I will go through the tips of the day again and send you a new pull request soon.

Yep, it can't be merged without conflicts.
Sorry for the delay with this pull request. Hope to hear from you.
I'm sorry, I got ill, it will take one or two weeks until you get the updated patch.
I finished my pull request, please use #132 instead of this one.
Update tip of the day, fix invalid menu items, shortcuts, typos
